It includes all sites which are permitted or have had permits.  It does not include non-permitted closed dumps.</abstract>    <purpose>This digital, geographically referenced data set was developed by the Iowa Department of Natural Resources to carry out agency responsibilities related to management, protection, and development of Iowa's natural resources.</purpose>    <supplinf>This replaces the coverage IOWASDS (Sanitary Disposal Sites).</supplinf>
